===Dictionary notes===
[[Category:Dictionary notes]]
*'''American Heritage Dictionary''' (via answers.com) and '''MSN Encarta Dictionary''' cover both senses but only mention the plural spelling.
*'''Collins Word Exchange''' has only the sense for the braid on an officer’s cap. It allows both the singular and plural spellings.
*'''Merriam-Webster Online''' has no entry.

